### Gradle dependency verification ###
# Binary keyring is a regenerable cache (./updateBaseline re-exports it).
# The reviewable ASCII gradle/verification-keyring.keys is committed instead so
# CI verifies signatures against local key material, not flaky public keyservers.
gradle/verification-keyring.gpg

